global.explanation: This JSON file represents a custom Keyforge adventure. To get a printable (therefore playable) version, upload it to https://customkeyforge.github.io/cardbuilder/#globalimportexport

cards.text:
The Ekwilibrium count is defined as the number of active player token creatures minus enemy token creatures.

Before a player turn starts, if the count is:
* 0 or 1 The active player steals one Equality token from the enemy.
* -2 or less, the enemy gains one Equality token.

**If the enemy has 4 Equality tokens per player, the players lose. If each player has at least 4 Equality tokens, the players win.**
cards.title: Shaky Ekwilibrium
